phrases: This is bad...
Very bad...
Subaru?
What is wrong?
Ah, I see.
This is where they suck you in.
No... Run!
Hurry!
Miso Natto
Nah, not natto.
Wait there...
That will be 363 yen.
Oh, a grooved-edge ten.
I am...
going to...
save you...
I guess anyone's eyes would be tired after holing up in their room, gaming all day.
What is going on?
This stuff obviously is not fake.
Which means...
So does this mean...
I have been summoned into a parallel world?!
I guess I can assume this is a fantasy world
with the typical medieval-style culture.
A realm where demihumans are commonplace,
and probably stuff like wars and adventures, as well.
And here, I am...
Hey!
Watch out!
This is it!
It is my turn!
This must be the event where I produce my first magic!
Look out!
Way to go!
Well done!
I guess I am not quite ready to use magic...
I cannot read this.
Hey, boy.
Those are some weird clothes.
Are you traveling?
What are these?
Those are appas.
They understand me, though.
The question is...
Huh?
What kind of money is that?
You cannot use that stuff in Lugunica.
That means you are flat broke, huh?
Get outta here!
Do not interfere with my business!
There is no other way...
I will just have to go around gathering information first.
This place is for demihumans only.
Ow!
I cannot... see...
Is this how it is supposed to be?
Was not I summoned into a parallel world?!
Where did my protagonist status go?!
Damn it.
(1)Contacts (2)Group Search (3)Abbreviations (4)New Contacts
City Hall Dad Mom Pizza
My cell phone still works...
Out of Range
But what is the point in having it?!
And my starting gear is way too wimpy!
You need a more substantial welfare program
to satisfy pressure-free generation kids like me!
I do not even have Excalibur or anything!
And besides, if I was summoned, where is the cute girl who summoned me?
Did she summon me only to leave me here alone?
Hey, is she finally here?!
The cute girl who summoned... me...
What are you babbling about?
If you do not want to get hurt, cough up whatever you have got!
Crap, it is a compulsory event...
Move it, move it!
You guys!
Out of my way!
Here we go!
Is that the cute girl who summoned me?!
Summoned?
I do not know what you are talkin' about, but I am busy!
Sorry!
Live strong!
Wait, what?
What?!
Hey, that did not make you decide to be less hostile toward me, by any chance, did it?
Actually, it rained on our parade and made things worse.
Yeah, of course...
Just calm down, Natsuki Subaru.
Since ancient times, it is the rule that anyone
summoned into a parallel world will display supernatural powers!
I will mow these guys down and make them fuel for my shining future!
You lumps of EXP!
That is the first time I ever hit someone!
I did not expect it to hurt me that much...
But this world is set up so that I will be strong!
My adrenaline is surging!
I have got this!
I am sorry!
It was all my fault!
Forgive me!
Spare me!
Play games with us, will you?!
Die, scum!
And do not think it will be painless!
That is enough.
Who the hell are you?!
Stop now, and I will let this slide.
So just graciously return what you stole.
What we stole?
Now, please.
It is important to me.
I will give up on the other stuff, but I cannot let you have that.
Be good and hand it over, please.
You did not come to save this kid?
What strange clothes he has...
If you asked me whether I had any connection to him, I would have to say no.
Then you have got no business with us!
If someone stole from you, it was that brat who just ran by!
Yeah!
That way!
She ran that way!
Hmm...
They do not seem to be lying...
I need to go after her!
But regardless of that...
I cannot overlook what is going on here.
Magic?
Mess with us, will you?!
I do not care if you can use magic!
I will kill you!
You think you can win when it is two against one?!
Huh?!
You are right.
Two against one may be unfair.
Two against two should make it fair, then.
You are a user of the spiritual arts?
Correct.
Back off now and I will not come after you.
Decide quick.
I am in a hurry.
You bitch!
Next time I see you, I will not go easy on you!
Do anything to her, and I will haunt you and your kin forever.
Not that you will have any kin if I do that.
You saved me.
Thanks.
Do not move.
See?
You averted your eyes because you have a guilty conscience!
Looks like my judgment was spot-on.
Are you sure?
I think it was just an instinctive male reaction.
I did not sense any malice at all.
You be quiet, Puck.
You know who stole my insignia from me, do not you?
Uh, sorry, but I do not have the slightest idea.
Huh?
Wait, it cannot be!
Did I really just come around the long way?
You should probably hurry after her, miss.
I could... help...
Aww, you should not have tried to get up.
What should we do?
It is none of our business.
He will not die.
We will just leave him.
Really?
Yes, really.
You say that, but I bet you will still help him.
I will not!
Yeah, right.
Absolutely not!
I am not going to save him!
She is even super cute when she is mad.
That is a parallel world fantasy for you...
Is my head on someone is lap?
You are awake?
I did not know cute girls were this hairy...
Wait, that cannot be right!
It is just a thoughtful arrangement we made
so you could at least feel happy until you woke up.
First of all, do not talk in that high voice!
No sane guy confuses a cat for the main heroine!
Aww, making myself bigger was worth it to see you so happy.
I am not happy!
I am sorry about this.
You stayed with me the whole time I was unconscious...
Do not get the wrong idea.
I had to stay because there are things I want to ask you.
Healing your wounds and making Puck your pillow until you woke up
were for my own benefit.
So I need you to repay me in kind.
For such a normal favor, you are making it sound like I really owe you big.
No such thing.
You have some idea who stole my insignia, right?
Insignia?
You mean one of those badge things that shows your affiliation?
It has a jewel in the center,
and it is about this big.
Sorry, but no matter how many times you ask me, I have no idea.
I see.
No helping that, then.
But you have given me the information that you know nothing,
and you gave me my answer, in return for healing you.
Huh?
Well, I am in a hurry, so I am going now.
Your wounds should be better now,
but next time, do not do dangerous things, like wandering into deserted alleys alone.
I am not concerned.
I am just warning you.
If that happens to you again, saving you will not be of any benefit to me,
so do not expect me to help.
Sorry about her.
She is so insincere.
Do not think badly of her.
Insincere?
I think this goes beyond that.
She was in such a hurry to find what was stolen from her,
yet she stopped to help me.
And she even came up with that lame excuse for a favor so I would not feel like I owed her,
even though I am a total stranger.
Anyone who lives like that...
is going to end up wasting their whole life!
Hey!
Wait up!
What?
Just so you know, I can only spend just a little more time with you.
I sense you are being a tiny bit lenient...
Forget that.
You lost something important, right?
Let me help you.
But you said you do not know anything...
But I remember her face, at least!
If I see her again, I will know!
You are very strange...
Just so you know, I cannot do anything to thank you.
I do not need you to.
I want to thank you.
That is why I want to help.
I did not do anything deserving of thanks.
I told you, I have already received compensation for healing your wounds.
Then...
I am going to help you for my own sake, too.
My objective is...
Let us see...
Yeah!
One good deed per day!
I do not sense any malice.
I think you can just accept his offer.
The more shields between yourself and ruffians, the better, after all.
That is what you want me around for?!
I mean it, though.
I cannot do anything to thank you.
No problem.
Just leave it to me!
I talked big, but is not this town too huge to find one little thing in?
It is the capital of Lugunica.
You did not even know that, um...
That is right.
We have not asked your name yet.
Should we all introduce ourselves?
Oh, yeah, you are right.
I will introduce myself first, then.
My name is Natsuki Subaru.
Not only am I clueless, I am also broke beyond compare!
Nice to meet ya!
When that is all you say, you really do sound hopeless.
And I am Puck!
Nice to meet you!
It is very unusual to see someone who can touch a spirit so casually.
Where are you from?
Well, following the usual pattern, a small island nation to the east.
Lugunica is the easternmost nation on our continental map.
There is no nation east of here.
No way, really?
There is nothing east of here?
You have no idea where you are, you have no money,
you cannot read, and you have no one who can help you.
You might be in an even more precarious position than me, um...
Subaru... was it?
Yes, that is my name.
But when I look at you this way, you look pretty well-built.
I do work out every day.
For a shut-in who is got to guard his house, that much is a given.
I am not sure I understand what a shut-in is,
but that means you are from a respectable family, right?
H-Hey
Your fingers, too.
They are very pretty.
They are evidence that you do not live like a peasant at all.
And your muscles do not look like the kind you gain by working.
Uh, anyway, I know your cat's name now,
but I have not heard yours yet.
My name?
Yeah.
I am...
Satella.
I have no family name.
You can just call me Satella.
I see... Satella...
That is a nice name.
You have terrible taste.
Okay, time to get back to asking around!
Hey, Subaru...
Do you get the feeling that child is lost?
Uh, but what about our questioning?
That is important too, but if she is lost, we have to do something.
I am in no place to talk after you saved me,
but do you understand the position we are in?
But...
She is crying!
Is she not, Subaru?
If you cannot do this with me, that is fine.
Thanks for all your help, Subaru.
I will handle it on my own from here,
after I help that little girl.
I am sorry I am not who you were looking for.
So, what is the matter?
Are not your mom and dad with you?
Um, uh...
Do not cry...
I will not do anything to you, okay?
What I have here is one grooved-edge ten-yen coin.
I will now clutch it tightly in my hand.
Tight, tight, tight... like that!
And now...
Imagine that!
And this... is where the coin was hiding.
You can have this.
It is rare, so take good care of it.
Thank you!
I see.
You got separated from your mom, huh?
Hey, it will be fine.
Just leave it to me and this young lady here.
We will find them for you in no time.
When we do this,
people who do not know us probably think we are a married couple and child, huh?
How embarrassing.
At best, I cannot see you as anything more than her older brother.
What makes you think I am that much younger than you?!
Oh!
Mommy!
Mommy!
Looks like she found her.
Yeah.
I am glad.
So...
I think we took a pretty long way around,
but what benefit will you insist that you got out of this?
That is easy.
Now we can continue our search with our minds at ease, right?
Anyway, why did you help me?
You were against the idea.
I could say I just wanted to show off my magic trick,
but that would be a lie.
I told you, finding your insignia will be my one good deed for the day!
Then, since you helped the little girl, is not your one good deed over?
That comeback was way too logical!
Come on, it does not hurt to do more than one nice thing in a day, right?
I just got tomorrow's out of the way.
My plan is to get a week's worth of good deeds taken care of early!
Subaru, you are the type that basically wastes your whole life, are not you?
You are the last one I want saying that to me.
You are not a bad boy, though.
Why are you treating me like I am younger than you again?
I doubt there is that much difference between us.
I do not think making guesses on that will help you.
I am a half-elf.
Now I get it.
No wonder I thought you were so cute!
Elves are always beautiful, right?
What?
What?
Well, I mean...
I am a half-elf...
Yeah, I heard you.
What did you do that for?
I just had to do something about this unbearable tingle I feel!
I cannot accept being hit for a reason like that.
Though I will forgive you because it was squishy.
I did not hit you out of anger or anything.
The opposite, in fact.
Subaru, you are such a dunderhead!
Dunderhead?
Who says that in this day and age?
And why are you insulting me?
Hmph!
Whatever!
More importantly, we have to get back to the search.
Hey, hang on!
Running around without a plan never ends well.
There is a basic rule of searches.
A basic rule of searches?
Yep.
You revisit the crime scene a hundred times.
Where was your insignia stolen?
So you see, it seems the crime happened right around here,
so I came back to this fruit stand after valiantly telling her to leave it all to me.
What?
I thought I had a customer, but it is just the broke kid?
Do you really want to take that attitude?
Have not you noticed I am not who I was before?
What?
Just look who I brought with me!
I brought someone who just might become a regular!
Um, Subaru...
You seem to have some weird expectations of me,
but I do not have any money, either.
Huh?!
Seriously?
So what did you want to say to me now that I have got two broke customers, boy?
We are actually looking for someone,
and we hoped we could ask you some questions...
That was a sarcastic way of telling you I do not have time for losers with no money!
Get outta here!
Mister!
Thanks for your help earlier.
What brings you back here?
It is my husband's shop, so we were just stopping by.
Husband?
Hey, there is my girl.
Wait, you know these broke losers?
She got lost, and they found her.
Here, lady.
Please accept it.
She wants to thank you in her own way.
Thank you.
Sorry about that.
You helped my daughter, and I want to thank you.
You can ask for anything.
There, you see?
That came back around and worked in our favor!
The air, the atmosphere, and most likely,
the attitudes of the people living here are awful.
Are you sure she is here?
It might be that Felt girl.
You said a nimble little blond girl, right?
She is well-known in the slums.
Do Not Know where she lives, though.
Maybe someone will tell us if we ask.
No one would sell out one of their own, so I do not think that would work.
Maybe we should come back later.
Whether you stay or leave, you should decide quickly.
I am almost out of time.
You are what?
Out of time?
I have a cute appearance, but I am a spirit.
It take a lot of mana just to appear in physical form.
So at night, I return to the crystal I was summoned from
and prepare for the emergence of the sun.
On average, my ideal staying time is from about nine to five.
Nine to five?
You sound like a civil servant.
Employment terms for spirits are more severe than I thought...
We will be fine without Puck.
We have to move forward.
Yeah.
But, sorry...
I am at my limit...
It is almost like he is dying when he disappears...
Sorry to work you so hard, Puck.
We will handle things from here, so get some rest.
Do not do anything reckless.
If it comes down to it, use the odo to summon me again.
Okay, take care of the rest, Subaru.
Hey, I have not been alone with a girl since I was in grade school!
Do not get any weird ideas.
I can use magic.
I will not!
The bigger issue is how we should find Felt now.
I will ask the lesser spirits.
Lesser spirits?
Lesser spirits are beings that have not become spirits yet.
They grow over time, and when they gain strength and self-awareness,
they become full spirits, like Puck.
